               steal<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183005270096"></xptr>ing, on the <rs id="t18300527-205-cd1084" type="crimeDate">29th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300527-205-off1083 t18300527-205-cd1084"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 1s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300527-205-victim1687" type="victimName">
                           Herbert 
